Template: printer-service/ws-url
Type: string
Description: WebSocket URL to connect to:
 The full WebSocket URL the printer service will connect to
 for receiving print jobs (e.g. wss://example.com/ws).

Template: printer-service/printer-mode
Type: select
Choices: usb, network, mock
Default: usb
Description: Printer connection mode:
 How the printer is connected to this device.
 .
  usb     - USB thermal printer (default)
  network - Network printer via TCP
  mock    - Console output for testing

Template: printer-service/network-ip
Type: string
Description: Network printer IP address:
 The IP address of the network printer (only used in network mode).

Template: printer-service/network-port
Type: string
Default: 9100
Description: Network printer port:
 The TCP port of the network printer (only used in network mode).
